# Ticket 2 - DNS Resolution Issue

## Scenario

Users attempting to access [www.wgu.edu](http://www.wgu.edu) were redirected to an unauthorized website.

## Investigation

### Tools Used

* DNS Manager
* nslookup
* host
* Browser Testing

### Commands

```bash
host www.wgu.edu
nslookup www.wgu.edu
```

### Findings

DNS resolution returned:

```text
10.10.20.20
```

which is a private IP address.

Research revealed the correct public destination was:

```text
151.101.155.52
```

## Root Cause

The DNS Host (A) record for [www.wgu.edu](http://www.wgu.edu) was configured with an incorrect IP address.

## Resolution

Updated the DNS record with the correct public IP address and verified successful name resolution.

## Skills Demonstrated

* DNS Troubleshooting
* DNS Administration
* Root Cause Analysis
* Name Resolution Testing

